And then what?

74
00:05:38,738 --> 00:05:41,400
我们已经进了屋里
We are already in the house.

75
00:05:41,574 --> 00:05:44,441
这些女人被绑起来 我们已犯下这宗罪行
Those women are bound. We have already committed this crime.

76
00:05:44,944 --> 00:05:47,003
就算离开也不会改变情况
We leave, it ain't gonna change any of that.

77
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:54,748
为什么这个青贮窖 不能出现在四下无人的地方？
Why couldn't there just be a silo in the middle of a field with no one around?

78
00:05:56,522 --> 00:05:58,717
我们可以想办法 去别的地方筹钱
We'll figure it out and get the money another way.

79
00:05:58,891 --> 00:06:01,553
对，也许我可以再去抢银行
Yeah, maybe I can rob another bank.

80
00:06:02,428 --> 00:06:04,953
查理曾经对我说过一句话
You know what Charles once said to me?

81
00:06:05,698 --> 00:06:08,724
他说犯了罪，一辈子都是犯人
He said there's no such thing as an ex-con.

82
00:06:09,802 --> 00:06:14,705
因为我以前还认为 我们可以洗清犯下的罪行
Because I used to think there was a way we could wipe the slate clean.

83
00:06:16,042 --> 00:06:18,203
弥补我们的罪恶
Make up for everything we've done.

84
00:06:21,547 --> 00:06:23,310
现在已经覆水难收，林克
The hat's over the wall, Linc.

85
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:28,219
大家都无法回头了
For everyone.

86
00:06:36,062 --> 00:06:38,963
我知道现在道歉于事无补
Sorry isn't gonna mean anything to you right now.

87
00:06:39,899 --> 00:06:41,423
但是我还是要说
But I wanna say it anyway.

88
00:06:43,870 --> 00:06:46,134
现在的情况不在计划之中
This wasn't supposed to happen.

89
00:06:48,341 --> 00:06:51,777
我们顶多一两小时就会离开
One or two hours, tops, and we'll be out of here.

90
00:06:51,944 --> 00:06:55,812
我保证，我们不会伤害你们
You have my word, no one will harm you.

91
00:06:58,785 --> 00:07:01,219
盯好她们
Keep your eyes open, okay?

92
00:07:01,954 --> 00:07:04,149
千万不能让她们受伤害
Nothing happens to them.

93
00:07:04,757 --> 00:07:06,122
绝对不能
Nothing.

94
