She should be. She was on the line with the governor when you walked up.

97
00:07:24,877 --> 00:07:26,174
你在监听
You were listening.

98
00:07:26,345 --> 00:07:28,813
两条线都装了窃听器 我们又不是新手
Both lines are tapped, We're not rookies,

99
00:07:28,981 --> 00:07:31,848
