- There are other people they care about, - The kid.

106
00:07:49,602 --> 00:07:51,092
罗杰
L.J.

107
00:07:51,637 --> 00:07:55,869
-州长的事，比尔K -保罗，专注在柏劳的儿子身上
- Now, in terms of the governor, Bill... - The Burrows kid, Paul.

108
00:07:56,042 --> 00:07:57,509
