Not much good in it. A lot of guilt.

149
00:10:54,086 --> 00:10:56,350
不过唯一的好处 就是告解
But the one good thing is confession.

150
00:10:57,857 --> 00:11:03,090
不管心里有什么让你难受 你只管说出来就好
Whatever you got eating at you, you just give it up.

151
00:11:03,863 --> 00:11:06,297
我得承认，这种感觉很不错
Feels good, I have to say.

152
00:11:07,633 --> 00:11:09,828
我想是因为说出来
Guess it's letting it out.

153
00:11:10,903 --> 00:11:14,862
-让另一个人听你告解 -我无话可说
- Letting another human being hear... - I got nothing to say to you, man.

154
00:11:20,946 --> 00:11:23,380
如果我告诉你一件事呢？
What if I told you something?

155
00:11:24,817 --> 00:11:27,445
一个无人知晓的秘密
A secret nobody else knows.

156
00:11:29,922 --> 00:11:31,389
奥斯卡席尔斯
Oscar shales.

157
00:11:38,130 --> 00:11:41,293
他是我几年前追捕的逃犯
A guy I was chasing a few years back.

158
00:11:42,334 --> 00:11:43,858
